data.description: Step into this 2bd, 2.5ba home. Enjoy the comfort of high ceilings & a cozy fireplace that creates an inviting atmosphere. This home boasts a multitude of upgrades including new life-proof luxury laminate flooring in the living room, tile floors in the kitchen, hallway & laundry room, a brand-new hot water heater to ensure your peace of mind. The kitchen is a delight with new recessed lighting, a stylish backsplash, granite countertops. Retreat to the master bedroom with a new ceiling fan & an impressive walk-in closet to keep your wardrobe organized. Additional luxuries include freshly painted walls throughout the downstairs. Outdoors, relish in your private, fenced in yard on your newly stained deck. Benefit from the convenience of a 2-car garage & appreciate the added value with no HOA
